      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING COLO (1) could manage only second at this track last time but turned heads when posting a quick 42.17 over 720m at this track the start prior. Hot win two back and looks the one to beat here. WOW ACE (4) finds it hard to win but looks close to breaking through. Has hit the frame at his last three runs, the latest finishing third (42.42) at this track. Has never been out of the money in three starts this course. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Leading player again. ZIPPING BILPIN (8) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing sixth (36.17) in a Grade 4/5 at Richmond. Solid record here winning two races. The form out of his last race has been franked. Bold showing expected. WINSOME STORM (6) can run a bold race on best form.",
